lead_paragraph: Yannick Agnel could still qualify for the Olympics after the 200 metres freestyle champion missed out following a possible touchpad blunder on Wednesday, the French swimming federation (FFN) said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Agnel May Get Chance to Defend Olympic Title-FFN
